<br>
This means every tell, every group msg, every auction , ooc . . . well you get it EVERYTHING :-)<br>
<br>
Whether you could sell this data I think probably not but I imagine you could get a good hand full of PhDs from grinding through this data.<br>
<br>
Here is humanity interacting and it is ALL capturable.<br>
<br>
Well at least verant agreed never to publish the things we say on line, oh wait they did not . . . <br>
<br>
I am just waiting for the first paper based on data from EQ <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
